    "The download page offers users the option to obtain all relevant gene and trait data materials.",
    "Additionally, a summary of data collection, processing, and integration is accessible on the help website (https://crop-gpa.aielab.net/help).",
    "There, users can find user guides and tutorials on how to navigate the browse, search, and tools functions, along with explanations for each page.",
    "In addition to the general functions, we developed a textmining tool to facilitate data integrity maintenance and keep up with updates conveniently.",
    "The tool GPA-BERT represents the ability to apply text mining techniques that extracts GPAs from the literature automatically, which helps deepen our current understanding of genephenotype interactions in a computable form."
